jdbcQuery.query:
select
i2.product_id as product_id, i2.time_id as time_id, i2.warehouse_id as warehouse_id, i2.store_id as store_id, i2.units_ordered as units_ordered, i2.units_shipped as units_shipped, i2.warehouse_sales as warehouse_sales, i2.warehouse_cost as warehouse_cost, i2.supply_time as supply_time, i2.store_invoice as store_invoice,
(i2.warehouse_sales - i2.warehouse_cost) as warehouse_profit
from inventory_fact_1998 i2
